The paper is about deep hashing methods for image retrieval, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of deep learning also suggests that it could be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper proposes a new algorithm that uses both pairwise label information and classification information, which is a common approach in supervised learning (cs.AI).
